&auml;htimallygy &yacute;okary bolsa, gan damarlaryny hirurgiki ta&yacute;dan
a&yacute;yrmak zerurdyr.&nbsp;Karotid arteri&yacute;any&#328; agyr daralmagy
insulty&#328; d&ouml;remegine seb&auml;p bolup biler.&nbsp;Gan damarlary
femoral arteri&yacute;any &yacute;apsa, a&yacute;ak &ouml;l&uuml;p
biler.&nbsp;&#350;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in k&ouml;plen&ccedil; gan damarlary
&uuml;&ccedil;in operasi&yacute;a gyssagly &yacute;erine
&yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Stentlemek&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
arteri&yacute;any&#328;&nbsp;<b>b&ouml;wetlenmegine&nbsp;</b>stent
go&yacute;ul&yacute;ar - g&auml;mini&#328; l&yacute;umenini has
gi&#328;eld&yacute;&auml;n we gan a&yacute;lany&#351;yny
erkinle&#351;dir&yacute;&auml;n &ccedil;ar&ccedil;uwany&#328; bir
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i.&nbsp;Stentde &yacute;&ouml;rite derman - antikoagulyant
bolup biler, bu &yacute;erde t&auml;ze gan damarlaryny&#328;
d&ouml;remegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni alar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&yacute;lanyp ge&ccedil;mek operasi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>, gany&#328; petiklenen &yacute;erden a&yacute;lanmagy
&uuml;&ccedil;in “a&yacute;lanyp ge&ccedil;mek” &yacute;ollaryny&#328; emele
