<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&#350;ar angi&yacute;oplastika&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>,
i&ccedil;ind&auml;ki gi&#328;el&yacute;&auml;n we &#351;ol bir wagty&#328;
&ouml;z&uuml;nde g&auml;mini&#328; l&yacute;umenini gi&#328;eld&yacute;&auml;n
g&auml;m&auml; in&ccedil;e turbany&#328; girizilmegi.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328;
hilini dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Stentasi&yacute;a
amallaryndan we &#351;u&#328;a me&#328;ze&#351; zatlardan so&#328;
dikeldi&#351; 1-2 hepde dowam ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Ertesi g&uuml;n
di&yacute;en &yacute;aly reabilitasi&yacute;a bejergisi hassany
i&#351;lem&auml;ge ba&#351;la&yacute;ar, onu&#328; wezipesi adamy adaty
durmu&#351;a doly ga&yacute;tarmak.&nbsp;&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
bejergisi durmu&#351; &uuml;&ccedil;in zerurdyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ownuk
g&auml;mileri&#328; &yacute;ok ediji keselleri bilen doly dikeltmek m&uuml;mkin
d&auml;l.&nbsp;Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini &yacute;okarlandyrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351; d&uuml;zg&uuml;nlerini berja&yacute; etmeli,
yzygiderli bejergi almaly we gan damarlaryna zy&yacute;anly faktorlara
du&ccedil;ar bolma&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin
kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Arteri&yacute;any&#328;
