i&yacute;mitlen&yacute;&auml;n b&ouml;legini&#328; nekrozyna seb&auml;p
bolar.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Her &yacute;agda&yacute;da &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykma ba&#351;ga&ccedil;a
bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>S&uuml;&yacute;ji keselini&#328; angi&yacute;opati&yacute;asy
trofiki &yacute;aralary&#328; we gangrenany&#328; d&ouml;remegine seb&auml;p
bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&yacute;aklardaky gan damarlaryny&#328; petiklenmegi
my&#351;salary&#328; spazmyna, nekrozlara we el-a&yacute;aklary&#328;
gangrenasyna seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; arteri&yacute;a trombozy i&#351;emi&yacute;a,
nekroz we peritonit keseline seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Karotid arteri&yacute;asyny&#328; b&ouml;wetlenmegi insulty&#328;
d&ouml;remegine seb&auml;p bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
aly&#351; &ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;ilim
&ccedil;ekmegi damar kesellerini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in zerur, &yacute;&ouml;ne &yacute;eterlik
d&auml;l.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le hem gl&yacute;ukoza, holesterin, LDL, &Yacute;LDL
we gan basy&#351;yny&#328; derejesine g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek
m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi okuwyndan
so&#328; az &yacute;agly i&yacute;mitlenmeli, gan basy&#351;yny, gan
gl&yacute;ukozasyny we holesterini peseltmek &uuml;&ccedil;in yzygiderli derman
i&ccedil;meli.&nbsp;Py&yacute;ada we a&ccedil;yk bedenterbi&yacute;e
&uuml;&ccedil;in has k&ouml;p wagt bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in durmu&#351;
&yacute;&ouml;relgesini &uuml;&yacute;tgetmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
